idth="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td colspan="2" valign="top" width="216"><div style="">(ii) A description of how the funds were used for the purposes reflected in this paragraph.</div></td><td valign="bottom" width="80"/></tr><tr><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td colspan="2" valign="top" width="216"><div style="">(iii) A description of the types of programs in which districts invested.</div></td><td valign="bottom" width="80"/></tr><tr><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td valign="top" width="24"/><td colspan="2" valign="top" width="216"><div style="">(iv) The number of students receiving mental health services on campus
